
Stay Safe Online Checklist:

- Never share your UPI PIN with anyone
- Always verify payment requests before accepting
- Do not click on unknown or suspicious links
- Use only official banking and UPI apps
- Enable SMS and app notifications for transactions
- Avoid sharing personal details online
- Double-check the receiver’s name before sending money
- Do not trust unknown calls claiming to be from banks

Reporting:
- National Cyber Crime Portal: https://cybercrime.gov.in
- Helpline Number: 1930
